  "detailed_description": "Explore a mythical ancient castle and solve puzzles to unfold the secrets of a deer people civilization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811040/extras/99c18df94f5e36ad0fc21ceec6306eaa.avif?t=1556205895\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br>Memoir is a puzzle game that reveals a story of a mythical ancient castle as you solve along. Guide the little deer kin as she wakes up at the entrance of a mythical ancient castle without memories.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811040/extras/48fe0a2f20d43fd92b81de89613c2056.avif?t=1556205895\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic push the block puzzles with a twist<br></li><li>Merge and eliminate blocks by merging them together to fit what the puzzle needs<br></li><li>Featuring more than 60+ puzzle levels<br></li><li>6 beautifully hand drawn ruins of a deer people civilization in different themes to explore</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Explore a mythical ancient castle and solve puzzles to unfold the secrets of a deer people civilization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811040/extras/99c18df94f5e36ad0fc21ceec6306eaa.avif?t=1556205895\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br>Memoir is a puzzle game that reveals a story of a mythical ancient castle as you solve along. Guide the little deer kin as she wakes up at the entrance of a mythical ancient castle without memories.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811040/extras/48fe0a2f20d43fd92b81de89613c2056.avif?t=1556205895\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic push the block puzzles with a twist<br></li><li>Merge and eliminate blocks by merging them together to fit what the puzzle needs<br></li><li>Featuring more than 60+ puzzle levels<br></li><li>6 beautifully hand drawn ruins of a deer people civilization in different themes to explore</li></ul>",
